{"tid":1696307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「譴責一切暴力」只適用於文明法治社會","createTime":"2019-11-06T06:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:04:16.000Z","uid":252657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"471d0fce07498fbf0aedc7b2d34616e71a5df06c","tid":1696307,"uid":252657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"To all 大愛朋友：<br />\n<br />\n現代社會以溝通妥協解決矛盾，是基於雙方擁有共同文明概念，同時以免卻原始以武力戰爭解決紛爭帶來嘅成本，做到最大化成效最小化成本。<br />\n<br />\n但若雙方沒有共同基礎概念，到最後所謂的 正/邪 對/錯，就是看誰的拳頭較硬。<br />\n<br />\n你若介定現在是戰爭時期，那就沒有甚麼「唔好再打會死人」，在戰場上基本沒有道德，只有我方/敵方，說到最尾就只有生或死。<br />\n<br />\n歷史是由勝利者寫下，如果咁鍾意靚畫面，唔緊要，你贏左先，到時你慢慢寫。<br />\n<br />\n#全民健身"},{"pid":"2b885173f1326bd4f6e077fbaf40a04b03e337c8","tid":1696307,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c464923b5caaa166f676ff78f153021a08d16c5a","tid":1696307,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"同意"}]}